abstract: PHILADELPHIA, Nov. 29 -- Army men around the world slept soundly tonight. Their future four-star generals beat Navy in football today, 27-0.

abstract: The New York State Theater's grand promenade will be turned into a bustling backstage scene on Dec. 8. Performers, directors, choreographers, designers and other City Center personnel have invited the public to a fund-raising bazaar there from 5 to 9 P.M. that day.
